{"tid":1284933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學老師因反送中面書言論被捕！","createTime":"2019-07-04T11:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T11:39:54.000Z","uid":253826,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e1e2efec2a7c60ac71c23000942e0096d6e9d6","tid":1284933,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"香港小學教師梁慧敏今日接受本報訪問，表示昨日（七月二號）被警察拘捕，罪名係「 威脅會摧毀或損壞財產  」， 所謂證據乃係梁慧敏曾在面書發表反送中等言論，例如「講咁多仲乜？下週立法會放雞尾酒啦！屌！ 」換言之，香港警方可以隨時以網言入人罪，違反言論自由。警方今日下晝開記招，透露經捕拘六男二女，年齡介乎十六歲至四十歲，涉網上公開警員資料、不誠實取用電腦及刑事損壞等行為，其中即包括梁慧敏。<br />\n警方昨日申請到搜查令，徹底搜查梁慧敏家，並且拍低大量私人空間照片，令其家人十分激動。<br />\n在差館落口供期間，警察曾向梁慧敏展示梁自己的面書頭像照片，其上印有「反修例 撤惡法」及「初一義士無罪」字句，問其有何政治目的？ 是否分享過涂謹申議員直播立法會審議逃犯條例的貼文？及貼文中「雞尾酒」何解？是否認識曾 like 或 share有關帖文的人？梁慧敏堅決行使保持箴默的權利。梁現已保釋，須於八月返差館報到，等睇律政會否起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongbilingualnews.com/post/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%EF%BC%81%E6%9B%BE%E7%84%AF%E6%96%87%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongbilingualnews.com%2Fpost%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%2584%25AF%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%258E&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=ddda0601\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongbilingualnews.com/post/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%EF%BC%81%E6%9B%BE%E7%84%AF%E6%96%87%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E</a>"},{"pid":"61535c547690a356981f52c9039aa0717f73c618","tid":1284933,"uid":205339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"吹歸英風加強國際壓力，引起國際關注<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284874</a>"},{"pid":"db0fe56ec5785245913389a89d09087af35424c2","tid":1284933,"uid":269221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"9f916cffafcb00db0de369100ce7adaa33ffab6d","tid":1284933,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"嚇鬼咩死黑警"},{"pid":"443c2032a8923f8286d6e0d2ab608388b64947cc","tid":1284933,"uid":272925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"0f75053687fde77013cc6d4b3c9d7840bb80f175","tid":1284933,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"請人飲酒都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8ad5bba3de9706315f87296588c2fd345bb032","tid":1284933,"uid":233453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 fb 打兩句都比人拉"},{"pid":"cd3656ed65d182ee5daf0f75afdc1065e16596ae","tid":1284933,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"做錯左一樣就係接受保釋"},{"pid":"da9ae9b4a1575c54c50e3601a1fcfe8477b8ca93","tid":1284933,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRC54wD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRC54wD.png&h=d8f17cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}